{"tid":2489691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗中王牌——印版F-35軍機自製計劃 力拚6至9年後量產","createTime":"2021-04-15T05:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T06:47:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"542865df6f87aa92eb861d055e050ef4d4e14f46","tid":2489691,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"印度自行開發設計的「先進中型戰機（Advanced Medium Combat Aircraft）」，可望在下半年獲得政府批准預算，將為其空軍（Indian Air Force）量身規劃「印度版F-35」，希望能力拚在2027至2030年間量產。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，印度「國防研究及發展組織（DRDO）」曾多次對先進中型戰機表達興趣，希望能盡速投入研發製造，印度政府有望在2021下半年批准「印度版F-35」戰機製造計劃，力拚2025年首飛，2027到2030年間量產的目標。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，前印度空軍司令巴達烏里亞（RKS Bhadauria）曾指出，他希望能在2032年前入手120架「先進中型戰機」，其中前2個中隊是早年的MK-1型，並搭載F/A-18E/F「超級大黃蜂」戰機同款的美製奇異F414發動機。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，剩下4個中隊的先進中型戰機MK-2型則將配置印度自行研發，推力增強的發動機，未來AMCA更有望整個部分六代機的科技，其中就包含了雷射武器，持續將其功能級戰力進行優化。<br />\n<br />\n報導也說，先進中型戰機具備「雷達隱形功能的5代機」，擁有雙引擎、重達25噸，內部彈艙可部署所有彈藥，並配有2台發動機，讓戰機能超音速巡航，定位會較像美軍F-35，大幅提升印度空軍攻擊力，除了自衛，也能成為與中國和巴基斯坦對抗的王牌機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3500393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3500393&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=7583fcc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3500393&h=3af9a4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3500393</a>"},{"pid":"9886040bcdf9baf559b6cfd052f71d51d114019c","tid":2489691,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"印度版F-35<br />\nSOR<br />\n忍唔到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53bcc6e9f5ed6ac0755879c9ed91c27a5012569","tid":2489691,"uid":225633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:34:54.000Z","msg":"想重新開一個三十年養老金計劃？毋忘光輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82f1966d5edf27bdda68cdd1ef8d8b75b44b7c6","tid":2489691,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"比架真嘅佢都抄唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63f5711bbb22b33b654c1b63fba9b5ad0f3891c","tid":2489691,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:43:05.000Z","msg":"LCA計劃都攪到成劈屎咁<br />\n仲話印度版F-35<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f696b0f9ed881494483e94421187b4ddaa4f96b","tid":2489691,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"咖哩製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印度空軍真係多國籍空軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又法製又俄製"}]}